      • getAbsoluteFactor

        public final double getAbsoluteFactor()
        Description copied from interface: UnitLiteral
        Get the absolute relationship between this literal and the ground literal. For example, in

        my_units: units (a, b => a * 10, c => b * 10)

        The factor for c is 10, but the absolute factor is 100.

        Specified by:
        getAbsoluteFactor in interface UnitLiteral
        Returns:
        conversion factor
